Class AeWSDLExtensionLoader

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def.AeWSDLExtensionLoader
public class AeWSDLExtensionLoader
extends java.lang.Object

Populates an extension registry with IO objects for reading and writing WSDL extensions to and from a WSDL document.
